{"tid":1601230,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"求救!  6s 6s 升上os13.1 開唔到機 (BOOTLOOP)","createTime":"2019-09-29T03:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T10:25:21.000Z","uid":223301,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9aa5c6207c216b7a3662119d58fd3d8e82a26fe1","tid":1601230,"uid":223301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:20:18.000Z","msg":"買左新機IP11, 係APPLE STORE諗住叫APPLE職員幫手過番舊機IP6s資料到新機, <br />\n<br />\nAPPLE職員話因為6S 個IOS版本太舊 (IOS 10.X )用唔到資料傳輸功能<br />\n要我自己係屋企UPDATE左IOS先<br />\n最後我清左8GB空間係電話&quot;軟件更新&quot;  直接UP 上IOS 13.X<br />\n更新進度條讀完就開唔返機 (白底黑APPLE LOGO, BOOTLOOP)<br />\n<br />\n我已經試過入RECOVERY MODE用ITUNES &quot;修復&quot; 功能再重裝IOS13.1<br />\n試左兩次, 情況都係一樣繼續BOOTLOOP<br />\n<br />\n我仲有咩方法可以自救到部6S 又可以保留資料?<br />\n<br />\n唔該各位!!"},{"pid":"21428c6aa52f1a28f6d73ec6b21657f4fa8c13da","tid":1601230,"uid":223301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:21:38.000Z","msg":"更新TITLE:<br />\n<br />\n求救! 6s 升上IOS 13.1 開唔到機 (BOOTLOOP)"},{"pid":"82d02bcae35a666794206c0ee977b052918c01ac","tid":1601230,"uid":223301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7d098f54f9a8b73efd8a6bb8139a388a0d9b6998","tid":1601230,"uid":13782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:08:47.000Z","msg":"都已經連電腦itunes直接用itunes備份再放落新機算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家一係試多幾次入dfu up ios ，一係就揾啲第三方軟件（imyfone)果類睇下可唔可以脫離recovery mode正常開機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90c6233176c76d7038c997eac716a835d1ff8b9","tid":1601230,"uid":223301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d098f54f9a8b73efd8a6bb8139a388a0d9b6998","tid":1601230,"uid":13782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:08:47.000Z","msg":"都已經連電腦itunes直接用itunes備份再放落新機算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家一係試多幾次入dfu up 